body:
Are you still worried about not being able to understand other people's conversations when playing on foreign servers? Come and try this mod!
This module can translate real-time chat conversations of other players.
1. The user end using this Mod will not translate the messages you send yourself;
2. You can choose to translate all information, including instruction prompts, etc;
3. It is easy to configure mod configuration in the modmenu;
4. Clicking on the translated message can switch between it and the original text;
5. Support translating the content sent by the current user into other languages;
6. Support custom APIs
7. After selecting 'Translate All Information', all information displayed in the chat box, such as command prompt messages, will be translated;
8. You can choose the target language for translation, etc.
